---
const funnel = [
  { stage: 'Applications reviewed', rate: '100%', detail: 'Every profile is screened by an engineer, not a keyword filter.' },
  { stage: 'Technical screening', rate: '31%', detail: 'Deep-dive interview on architecture, code decisions, and communication.' },
  { stage: 'Paid test project', rate: '9%', detail: 'A realistic task evaluated for quality, speed, and collaboration style.' },
  { stage: 'Join the network', rate: '3%', detail: 'Only engineers we would put on our own projects make it into the network.' },
];
---

<section class="ink-panel">
  <div class="container mx-auto">
    <div class="grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[0.9fr,1.45fr] lg:items-start">
      <div class="lg:sticky lg:top-28">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-signal sm:text-sm">03 — Vetting</p>
        <h2 class="mt-4 font-headline text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight sm:text-6xl">
          Only <span class="text-signal">3%</span> make it in
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-ink-foreground/70">
          "Pre-vetted" has a specific meaning here: by the time you meet a candidate, technical ability, communication, and delivery habits have already been tested.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 border-t border-ink-foreground/20 pt-6">
          <p class="font-headline text-lg font-bold">Your first interview should feel like a final screen.</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-ink-foreground/70">
            We optimize for fewer, stronger introductions instead of sending a large resume batch for your team to sort through.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <ol class="border-t border-ink-foreground/20">
        {funnel.map((step) => (
          <li class="grid gap-x-8 gap-y-3 border-b border-ink-foreground/20 py-8 sm:grid-cols-[10rem,1fr] sm:py-10">
            <div>
              <p class="font-mono text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight text-signal sm:text-5xl">{step.rate}</p>
              <p class="mt-1.5 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-ink-foreground/60">pass point</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold sm:text-2xl">{step.stage}</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 leading-7 text-ink-foreground/70">{step.detail}</p>
              <div class="mt-5 h-1.5 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-ink-foreground/10" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="h-full rounded-full bg-signal" style={`width: ${step.rate}`}></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </li>
        ))}
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
